{"tid":1277994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望各位連登仔得閒就練下寫字","createTime":"2019-07-02T10:34:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:34:53.000Z","uid":27146,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9e97fae25a9f66140e2d5b76aac5b021745f1086","tid":1277994,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:34:36.000Z","msg":"發覺最近經常聽倒啲人話啲後生仔(示威者)寫字寫到小學生咁，完全唔似讀過書之類既廢話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然讀得書多同寫字靚唔靚無直接關係，但係字體公整真係會比人感覺良好，有修養有文化，各位寫出黎既標語都有機會比傳媒影倒，唔只比廢老睇，仲有日本，台灣呢啲識睇漢字既地方，所以其實得閒練下字絕對可以增加大眾既好感度，手字唔一定要靚到好似寫書法咁，只要簡簡單單整整齊齊就可以。<br />\n<br />\n成本好低，只要拎張廢紙拎起支筆得閒拎黎寫下字就可以<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9749c1fea14990cdd1c586fe22a30745be7a247b","tid":1277994,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:37:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"248ac95892e13a705b6dfaa39f2a9d3baf93772c","tid":1277994,"uid":148185,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:40:32.000Z","msg":"搬左成日野又跑黎跑去<br />\n成身冇力又手震點寫得靚呀清"},{"pid":"a01960a8aef731fc686467687e8952bf5f91b10e","tid":1277994,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T10:42:28.000Z","msg":"係lol<br />\n寫字太醜比人認就唔好啦"},{"pid":"d2dfe4c1f5502f7eb8ab7776476279c8a1b2b673","tid":1277994,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"